column5: Walleye opener in zone 20 this Saturday...  Anybody got plans??  I'm heading out Friday night and lines are goin in  at 12:01am!!!
I would say let's hook up, but two problems are in my way.  1, you are not close to me.  2, it's my 11 year wedding anniversary so I think she won't be to happy with me if I make fishing plans...
Being boatless I forgot all about the opener this weekend.  Makes it easier if I put it out of my mind.  That being said, anyone need a netman Sunday???

Anniversary every walleye opener?  I would get a divorce then re-marry in let's say winternet season. Life is all about solutions.  Problem is this - 1/2 of a 1/2 plus the original 1/2 = 3/4.   That is 1/4 for you.  You would definately have to be on your best behaviour after the adjustment.
I'm screwed so I HAVE to miss it...
